![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578252182133-FFQX8P7H2SDKRV6ASO0R/image-asset.jpeg)

With Endgame right around the corner the gang gets nostalgic in our BIGGEST episode of the year (until next week lol). Taking a fresh look at Avengers (2012), and the MCU this episode of Major Issues tries to follow the journeys of each character through phase one and their impacts on the juggernaut that is the Marvel Cinematic Universe. Full of awesome trivia, fun facts and heated opinions, this episode serves as an amazing precursor to Avenger's Endgame and a teary-eyed trip down memory lane.

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
